        "synopsis": {
            "value": "A story between an ordinary girl who rescues a downtrodden CEO who has lost his memories, thus beginning a dreamy fairy tale.\n\nShan Jun Hao is the CEO of Senwell. He's a hard-hitting leader who never takes half measures to achieve what he wants. His encounter with Ye Qian Yu is not a pleasant one as he has mandated the closure of the Guanmei Inn, a place that Ye Qian Yu holds\n\ndear. When Shan Jun Hao gets into an accident and wakes up with no memories of the past, Ye Qian Yu takes him in and gives him a fake identity. They grow closer through their time together even though she knows that one day, he is bound to leave.",
            "source": "mydramalist",
            "source_link": "https://mydramalist.com/39955-frog-prince"
